msgid "Subheadings break long content into scannable sections."
msgstr "Zwischenüberschriften unterteilen lange Inhalte in übersichtliche Abschnitte."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add 2–8 H2/H3 headings that summarize key sections."
msgstr "Fügen Sie 2–8 H2/H3-Überschriften hinzu, die wichtige Abschnitte zusammenfassen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves readability and keeps users engaged longer."
msgstr "Verbessert die Lesbarkeit und hält Benutzer länger engagiert."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in a subheading reinforces the main topic."
msgstr "Das Einbeziehen der Schlüsselphrase in eine Unterüberschrift verstärkt das Hauptthema."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Place the focus keyphrase in one relevant H2 or H3."
msgstr "Platzieren Sie die Fokus-Schlüsselphrase in einem relevanten H2 oder H3."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps search engines connect sections to the main theme."
msgstr "Hilft Suchmaschinen, Abschnitte mit dem Hauptthema zu verbinden."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "The opening paragraph sets context for both users and search engines."
msgstr "Der einleitende Absatz gibt sowohl Nutzern als auch Suchmaschinen Kontext."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus keyphrase once in the first 1–2 sentences."
msgstr "Verwenden Sie die Fokus-Schlüsselphrase einmal in den ersten 1–2 Sätzen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger topical clarity can improve relevance signals."
msgstr "Stärkere thematische Klarheit kann Relevanzsignale verbessern."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keyphrase density shows how often the main topic appears."
msgstr "Schlüsselphrasen-Dichte zeigt, wie oft das Hauptthema erscheint."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the keyphrase naturally throughout the content without stuffing."
msgstr "Verwenden Sie die Schlüsselphrase natürlich im gesamten Inhalt, ohne Keyword-Stuffing."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Balanced usage supports relevance while avoiding spam signals."
msgstr "Ausgewogene Nutzung unterstützt Relevanz und vermeidet Spam-Signale."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long-tail phrases capture more specific search intent."
msgstr "Long-Tail-Phrasen erfassen spezifischere Suchabsichten."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add your long-tail phrases where they fit naturally in sections."
msgstr "Fügen Sie Ihre Long-Tail-Phrasen dort hinzu, wo sie natürlich in die Abschnitte passen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps the page rank for more specific queries."
msgstr "Hilft der Seite, für spezifischere Anfragen zu ranken."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Very short pages often lack depth to satisfy readers."
msgstr "Sehr kurzen Seiten fehlt oft die Tiefe, um Leser zufriedenzustellen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Expand the content with examples, steps, or FAQs."
msgstr "Erweitern Sie den Inhalt mit Beispielen, Schritten oder FAQs."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "More complete content tends to perform better for informational queries."
msgstr "Vollständigere Inhalte neigen dazu, bei informativen Suchanfragen besser abzuschneiden."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Readable content keeps users engaged and reduces bounce."
msgstr "Lesbarer Inhalt hält Benutzer engagiert und reduziert die Absprungrate."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Shorten sentences, use simpler words, and break up long paragraphs."
msgstr "Kürzen Sie Sätze, verwenden Sie einfachere Wörter und teilen Sie lange Absätze auf."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improved clarity boosts dwell time and user satisfaction."
msgstr "Verbesserte Klarheit steigert Verweildauer und Benutzerzufriedenheit."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long sentences are hard to read in CJK languages."
msgstr "Lange Sätze sind in CJK-Sprachen schwer zu lesen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Split long sentences and add punctuation for clearer flow."
msgstr "Teilen Sie lange Sätze auf und fügen Sie Satzzeichen für einen klareren Fluss hinzu."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clearer reading experience helps users stay on the page."
msgstr "Klareres Leseerlebnis hilft Benutzern, auf der Seite zu bleiben."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Images support understanding and break up long text."
msgstr "Bilder unterstützen das Verständnis und unterbrechen lange Texte."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add at least one relevant image that illustrates the topic."
msgstr "Fügen Sie mindestens ein relevantes Bild hinzu, das das Thema veranschaulicht."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Visuals improve engagement and can help with image search."
msgstr "Visuelle Elemente verbessern das Engagement und können bei der Bildersuche helfen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Alt text helps search engines and screen readers interpret images."
msgstr "Alt-Text hilft Suchmaschinen und Bildschirmleseprogrammen, Bilder zu interpretieren."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Describe each image in plain language, focusing on what it shows."
msgstr "Beschreiben Sie jedes Bild in einfacher Sprache und konzentrieren Sie sich darauf, was es zeigt."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves accessibility and adds extra relevance signals."
msgstr "Verbessert die Zugänglichkeit und fügt zusätzliche Relevanzsignale hinzu."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Spacing long-tail phrases prevents keyword stuffing."
msgstr "Abstände zwischen Long-Tail-Phrasen verhindern Keyword-Stuffing."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Spread similar phrases across different sections."
msgstr "Verteilen Sie ähnliche Phrasen über verschiedene Abschnitte."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keeps content natural while still covering long-tail queries."
msgstr "Hält den Inhalt natürlich und deckt dennoch Long-Tail-Anfragen ab."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in one image alt text reinforces the topic."
msgstr "Das Einbeziehen der Schlüsselphrase in einem Bild-Alt-Text verstärkt das Thema."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus phrase in a single relevant image alt description."
msgstr "Verwenden Sie die Fokus-Phrase in einer einzigen relevanten Bild-Alt-Beschreibung."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Adds topical relevance without over-optimizing every image."
msgstr "Fügt thematische Relevanz hinzu, ohne jedes Bild zu überoptimieren."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Internal links help users and search engines discover related pages."
msgstr "Interne Links helfen Benutzern und Suchmaschinen, verwandte Seiten zu entdecken."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Link to 1–3 relevant posts or pages using descriptive anchor text."
msgstr "Verlinken Sie zu 1–3 relevanten Beiträgen oder Seiten mit beschreibendem Ankertext."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves site structure and can pass authority to key pages."
msgstr "Verbessert die Website-Struktur und kann Autorität an Schlüsselseiten weitergeben."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "External links show credibility and provide references."
msgstr "Externe Links zeigen Glaubwürdigkeit und bieten Referenzen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add at least one trusted source link that supports your content."
msgstr "Fügen Sie mindestens einen vertrauenswürdigen Quellenlink hinzu, der Ihre Inhalte unterstützt."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Builds trust and can improve perceived quality."
msgstr "Baut Vertrauen auf und kann die wahrgenommene Qualität verbessern."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Rel attributes clarify how external links should be treated."
msgstr "Rel-Attribute klären, wie externe Links behandelt werden sollen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add rel values like nofollow, sponsored, or ugc where appropriate."
msgstr "Fügen Sie rel-Werte wie nofollow, sponsored oder ugc hinzu, wo angemessen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps avoid link spam signals and keeps compliance clean."
msgstr "Hilft, Link-Spam-Signale zu vermeiden und die Compliance sauber zu halten."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Short, readable URLs are easier to understand and share."
msgstr "Kurze, lesbare URLs sind einfacher zu verstehen und zu teilen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use 2–5 words that match the topic and remove stop words."
msgstr "Verwenden Sie 2–5 Wörter, die zum Thema passen, und entfernen Sie Stoppwörter."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clean URLs improve clarity and can increase click confidence."
msgstr "Saubere URLs verbessern die Klarheit und können das Klickvertrauen erhöhen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the focus phrase in the URL reinforces relevance."
msgstr "Das Einbeziehen der Fokusphrase in die URL verstärkt die Relevanz."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add the focus keyphrase to the slug without extra filler."
msgstr "Fügen Sie die Fokus-Schlüsselphrase zum Slug hinzu, ohne zusätzliche Füllwörter."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Strengthens topical signals and makes URLs clearer."
msgstr "Stärkt thematische Signale und macht URLs klarer."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Canonical URLs tell search engines which version to index."
msgstr "Kanonische URLs teilen Suchmaschinen mit, welche Version indexiert werden soll."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Ensure the canonical points to the main URL of the page."
msgstr "Stellen Sie sicher, dass das Canonical auf die Haupt-URL der Seite zeigt."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Prevents duplicate content issues and consolidates ranking signals."
msgstr "Verhindert Duplicate-Content-Probleme und konsolidiert Ranking-Signale."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Article schema helps search engines understand your content type."
msgstr "Artikel-Schema hilft Suchmaschinen, Ihren Inhaltstyp zu verstehen."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
